original_title: Habitat / AWS - Regal Road / Kalis in Mono
overview: Regal Road was a short promo DVD that highlighted Habitat's twelve day UK tour through London, Bristol, Nottingham and Edinburgh. Starring Fred Gall, Stefan Janoski, Raymond Molinar, Ed Selego, Silas Baxter-Neal and UK rider Will Ainley.  Kalis In Mono was a short promo DVD which included a full length Josh Kalis part. This footage was intended for Mind Field, but after Mind Field's release got pushed back, this promo was released to avoid the footage from getting old.
title: Habitat / AWS - Regal Road / Kalis in Mono
